| `tools` | array | ‚úÖ Yes | - | Array of tool objects. For web search, must include the web_search tool configuration. |
| `stream` | boolean | ‚ùå No | `false` | Whether to stream the response |
| `temperature` | number | ‚ùå No | `1.0` | Amount of randomness injected into the response. Ranges from 0.0 to 1.0 |
| `top_p` | number | ‚ùå No | `1.0` | Use nucleus sampling. Ranges from 0.0 to 1.0 |
| `max_tokens` | integer | ‚ùå No | - | The maximum number of tokens to generate before stopping |
| `stop` | array | ‚ùå No | - | Custom text sequences that will cause the model to stop generating |

### Messages Array Structure

Each message object in the `messages` array should have the following structure:

| Field | Type | Required | Description |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| `role` | string | ‚úÖ Yes | The role of the message. Can be: `user`, `assistant`, or `system` |
| `content` | array/string | ‚úÖ Yes | The content of the message |

### Content Array Structure (when content is an array)

| Field | Type | Required | Example | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `type` | string | ‚úÖ Yes | `text` | The type of content |
| `text` | string | ‚úÖ Yes | `"What's the weather in NYC?"` | The text content when type is `text` |

### Tools Array Structure

For web search functionality, the `tools` array should contain a web search tool object:

| Field | Type | Required | Example | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `type` | string | ‚úÖ Yes | `web_search` | The type of tool. Must be `web_search` for web search |
| `max_uses` | integer | ‚ùå No | `5` | Maximum number of times the web search tool can be used in a single request |
| `allowed_domains` | array | ‚ùå No | `["example.com", "trusteddomain.org"]` | Only include search results from these domains |
| `blocked_domains` | array | ‚ùå No | `["untrustedsource.com"]` | Never include search results from these domains |

#### Max Uses

The `max_uses` parameter limits the number of searches performed. If Claude attempts more searches than allowed, the web search result will be an error with the `max_uses_exceeded` error code.

#### Domain Filtering

When using domain filters:

- Domains should not include the HTTP/HTTPS scheme (use `example.com` instead of `https://example.com`)
- Subdomains are automatically included (`example.com` covers `docs.example.com`)
