| `max_tokens` | integer | ‚úÖ Yes | - | 1-64000 | Maximum number of tokens to generate. The model may stop before reaching this limit |
| `tools` | array | ‚úÖ Yes | - | - | Array of tool objects. For web search, must include the web_search tool configuration with type `web_search_20250305` |
| `temperature` | number | ‚ùå No | `1.0` | 0.0-1.0 | Controls randomness in output. Use lower values (closer to 0.0) for analytical tasks, higher values (closer to 1.0) for creative tasks. Note: Even at 0.0, results are not fully deterministic |
| `top_p` | number | ‚ùå No | - | 0.0-1.0 | Nucleus sampling threshold. Controls diversity by considering only tokens with cumulative probability up to top_p. Recommended for advanced use only. Do not use with temperature |
